# Allow OpenCode's ripgrep search to inspect directories normally filtered by .gitignore.
# These negated patterns keep key dependency/build trees visible during agent runs.

# Dependencies and vendored sources
!**/node_modules/**
!vendor/**

# Build output and generated artifacts
!**/dist/**
!**/build/**
!**/dist-electron/**
!src-tauri/target/**
!apps/server/server/**
